## 八、ERP 推送接口 (DA/T 104 合规版)

为了满足 **DA/T 104-2024** 标准及实时归档需求，系统提供标准化的 "Push" 接口，允许 ERP 系统主动推送会计资料 SIP 包。

### 1. 接收归档信息包 (Receive SIP)

*   **URL**: `/api/integration/erp/receive-sip`
*   **Method**: `POST`
*   **Content-Type**: `application/json` (推荐) 或 `application/xml`
*   **Auth**: Bearer Token (需申请专用集成 Token)

#### 请求参数 (JSON 示例)

```json
{
  "source_system": "Yonyou_U8C", // 来源系统标识
  "batch_id": "BATCH_20231027_001", // 批次号 (可选)
  "vouchers": [
    {
      "voucher_id": "V-202310-001", // 来源系统唯一ID
      "voucher_date": "2023-10-27",
      "voucher_type": "记账凭证",
      "summary": "报销差旅费",
      "total_amount": 1250.00, // 必须为数字，两位小数
      "entries": [
        {
          "summary": "张三差旅费",
          "account_code": "6602",
          "account_name": "管理费用",
          "debit_amount": 1250.00,
          "credit_amount": 0.00
        },
        {
          "summary": "银行付款",
